task.summary: Added DialogWrapper and DialogModule to dynamically display data
Changed layout; added user detail button; moved login/logout to sidebar menu
Return invalid credentials error if user doesn't exist
Added ErrorHandlingService; functionality for display errors returned over http
Switched sidenav, toolbar and parts of auth to angular-material; added intendedRoute to AuthLogin
Removed 'deactivated' property from transactions, replaced with soft deletes
Added options to CRUD's '/list' to control the order of the list
Added CollectorModule to bundle all MatModules
Remade auth components with angular material
Added FinAddComponent functionality with auto completion
Adjusted positioning and size of router outlet
Completed display of accounts in tree, ordered by category
Added default value for timestamp because... MySQL
Added AlertDialogModule for generic dialogs like confirmation
Added deleting accounts; moved options to dropdown menu
fix(crud-constructor): limit and order now work together
feat(crud-constructor): option for bypassing soft deletes on list
feat(fin-transaction): more validation and feedback on submit
